OUT! TAKEN ON THE SECOND ATTEMPT! Heartbreak for Markram as he falls 4 short of what would have been another brilliant ton. This shot was not needed but the eagerness of getting to the ton has probably got to him. He looks to play the paddle scoop. This is very full from Gudakesh Motie. It lobs of the toe-end behind the keeper. Jermaine Blackwood at slip runs to his left and takes it after a juggle. Motie has his second, he has not bowled well but has two. Markram walks back to a standing ovation. Can Windies now build on this?
Howout: c Jermaine Blackwood b Gudakesh Motie

OUT! BOWLED! That was the wicket South Africa were looking for. Excellent from Coetzee. This is on a length and around off, nips in and stays very low. Da Silva defends the wrong line, gets beaten on the outside edge and it pings the off pole.
Howout: b Gerald Coetzee

Commentary: Bouncer on off, Joseph sits down.
Flat and on middle, Roach defends it out.
This is full and on off, blocked out.
This one lands on middle and stays low. Roach blocks.
Full and on middle, spins down the leg side. Roach misses his flick.
On middle, Roach inside edges his flick onto the pads and it goes over the man at leg slip.
On middle, Roach goes back and defends.
FOUR! Superb shot! Length ball, outside off, Joseph drives in the gap through covers for four.
A bumper on middle, Joseph evades.
Length and on off, pushed to mid-wicket.
Short and on off, Joseph lets it go.
This is down the leg side, Joseph fails to clip it away.
Length and on off, this shoots off the deck. Joseph looks to defend but goes off the shoulder of the bat over the slip cordon for one.
DROPPED! Full and on off, Joseph slogs it high and to deep mid-wicket. Kagiso Rabada has enough time to adjust and he takes onto his left but fails to hold on.
On middle, Roach bunts it to square leg for one.
SIX! This time it is clean! Fuller and outside off, spins in. Joseph heaves it over deep mid-wicket for a six.
On middle, blocked out.
SIX! Joseph is not shy! Too full and outside off. Joseph drags and hits it over mid-wicket for a biggie.
Tossed up on off, defended out.
Length and outside off, Roach looks to push but misses.
Around off, pushed to cover.
On a length and on middle, blocked out.
This is short and way outside off, Roach swings and misses.
OUT! TAKEN! South Africa are one wicket away! Shorter and outside  off, Roach swings his bat without much effort and gets a top edge to third man where Keegan Petersen (sub) takes it low and sharp.
Howout: c sub Keegan Petersen b Gerald Coetzee

Commentary: This is outside off, Motie has a poke at it but misses.

OUT! STUMPED! That is it! This is full and outside off, Joseph comes down the track to heave but misses. The keeper though is quick to remove the bails. Joseph tries to come back in but is too late. What a performance by the home team. SOUTH AFRICA WIN BY 284 RUNS.
Howout: st Heinrich Klaasen b Simon Harmer
